    <pre>Hi mac9416! Thanks for filing this bug.

They're for up-voting particularly good answers, or particularly bad ones. This 
way, if people see that their answer has been down-voted, they can think about 
rephrasing it to make it better.

We'll try to make that clearer.</pre>
